title: The title of hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', now it changes with settings.
OB: The title of the hyperlink builder is changing based on the settings.
EB: The title of the hyperlink builder should always be 'Hyperlink Options', regardless of the settings.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Set a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'.
2. Observe the title of the hyperlink builder.
